            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/632.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Return</strong> the reserved pan to a medium-high heat and add the spring onion and ginger with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> vegetable oil and cook for 1 min</p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> the sweet chilli stock and transfer the chicken back to the pan</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cook</strong> for 3-5 min or until your chicken is cooked through and your sauce is sticky and has thickened</p>",
